# Azure AI Search Configuration
# Azure AI Search 設定
AZURE_SEARCH_ENDPOINT=https://your-search-service.search.windows.net
AZURE_SEARCH_API_KEY=your-search-api-key-here
AZURE_SEARCH_INDEX=vector-search-quickstart

# Azure AI Project Configuration  
# Azure AI Project 設定
PROJECT_ENDPOINT=https://your-ai-project.cognitiveservices.azure.com
MODEL_DEPLOYMENT_NAME=gpt-4o

# Optional: Alternative authentication (if not using API key)
# 可選：替代認證方式（如果不使用 API 金鑰）
# AZURE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id
# AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret
# AZURE_TENANT_ID=your-tenant-id

# Instructions for setup:
# 設定說明：
# 1. Copy this file to .env (複製此文件為 .env)
# 2. Fill in your actual Azure service endpoints and keys (填入您的 Azure 服務端點和金鑰)
# 3. Make sure .env is in your .gitignore to keep credentials secure (確保 .env 在 .gitignore 中以保護憑證安全)